# Thesis Writing (Condensed)

**Purpose:** Write PhD/Master's thesis chapters.

**Links to:** paper-writing, sota-survey, research-design, experiment-tracking, technical-english-cs

---

## Structure (6 chapters)

1. Introduction (10-15p): background, problem, objectives, RQs, contributions
2. Literature Review (20-30p): taxonomy, detailed analysis, comparison table, gaps
3. Methodology (15-25p): formulation, system overview, components, complexity
4. Experiments (15-20p): setup, datasets, baselines, results, ablation, analysis
5. Discussion (5-10p): interpretation, implications, limitations, validity threats
6. Conclusion (3-5p): contributions summary, RQ answers, future work

## Key Differences from Paper

| Aspect | Paper | Thesis |
|--------|-------|--------|
| Length | 8-12p | 150-250p |
| References | 30-50 | 100-200 |
| Related Work | 1-2p | 20-30p |
| Method detail | Concise | Exhaustive |
| Proofs | Sketch | Full |

## Chapter 2 Template (Literature Review)

2.1 Overview (2-3p)
2.2 Theoretical Foundations (3-5p)
2.3 Taxonomy (2-3p): Group A, B, C by approach
2.4 Key Works Analysis (8-12p): problem, method, strengths, limitations
2.5 Comparison Table
2.6 Research Gaps → map to RQs

## Chapter 3 Template (Methodology)

3.1 Problem Formulation: notation, objective, constraints, assumptions
3.2 System Overview: architecture diagram, components, data flow
3.3-3.4 Components: motivation, algorithm, pseudocode, complexity
3.5 Theoretical Analysis: convergence, optimality
3.6 Complexity Table

## Chapter 4 Template (Experiments)

4.1 Setup: hardware, software, hyperparameters
4.2 Datasets table
4.3 Baselines table
4.4 Main Results table + analysis
4.5 Ablation table
4.6 Sensitivity: hyperparameter, convergence, scalability
4.7 Answer RQs with evidence

## Vietnamese Format

Abstract: Tóm tắt (background → problem → method → results → contributions)
Chapters: Chương 1-6

## LaTeX

\documentclass[12pt,a4paper]{report}
\usepackage[utf8]{vietnam}
\chapter{}, \section{}, \subsection{}
\bibliographystyle{plain}
